OL,3,CJay Cartmell: Man appears at court
OL,4,Ccharged with gross negligence
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FA man from Cleator Moor made his first
OL,8,Fappearance in court today charged with
OL,9,Fthe unlawful killing of an eight-year-
OL,10,Fold boy.
OL,12,FAllan Thursby, 64, spoke only to
OL,13,Fconfirm his name, address and date of
OL,14,Fbirth at Carlisle Magistrates' Court
OL,15,Fin a hearing which lasted less than
OL,16,Ffive minutes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
