OL,3,CJay Cartmell: Man appears at court
OL,4,Ccharged with gross negligence
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FThursby was not asked to enter a plea,
OL,8,Fand was bailed to appear at Carlisle
OL,9,FCrown Court for a plea and trial
OL,10,Fpreparation hearing on the April 24 at
OL,11,F10:30.
OL,13,FHe was warned that if he failed to
OL,14,Fturn up he would be committing an
OL,15,Foffence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
