OL,3,CJay Cartmell: Man appears at court
OL,4,Ccharged with gross negligence
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FThursby is accused of gross negligence
OL,8,Fmanslaughter, after Jay Cartmell
OL,9,Fsustained serious injuries in an
OL,10,Fincident involving the discharge of a
OL,11,Ffirearm on land near Warcop, Cumbria,
OL,12,Fon September 28 2024.
OL,14,FThe youngster, from Frizington,
OL,15,FCumbria, was rushed to hospital by air
OL,16,Fambulance but was later pronounced
OL,17,Fdead.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
