OL,3,CJay Cartmell: Man appears at court
OL,4,Ccharged with gross negligence
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FThe court heard gross negligence
OL,8,Fmanslaughter is an indictable only
OL,9,Foffence and cannot be tried at a
OL,10,Fmagistrates' court.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Philip Holden imposed a
OL,13,Fbail condition that Thursby must not
OL,14,Fcontact Jay's parents.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
